Invocation Name: automotive electrical game
des:
Alexa quizzes you on ASE electrical questions. Provide the answer and try to achieve a high score.
This skill was created as a free source to help students enrolled in automotive service technology classes prepare themselves for the student ASE certification test. It will also be helpful for professional technicians or automotive enthusiasts.
